title: God of War Ragnarok: The Mythology Behind the End of the World

media:group.media:title: God of War Ragnarok: The Mythology Behind the End of the World
media:group.media:description: Ragnarök is coming, and Kratos and Atreus will soon find themselves facing the end of the world itself. Yet, as the great battle with the most dangerous of Aesir approaches, let’s look at the history of behind the Norse apocalypse, Ragnarok itself, to see what that might mean for God of War Ragnarok.
